title: 2023 Cycling World Championships: Great Britain's Katie Archibald, Laurie Greenland & Eleanor Barker in action

maintext:
Post
The lights have gone out on another pretty productive evening for Great Britain on the track.
I mean it was raining gold and silver medals at one point.
So if you fancy a quick recap here you go.
Alternatively you can read my colleague Joe Rindl's, external report which covers everything track related and plenty more from day two of the Cycling World Championships in Glasgow.
Thanks for sticking with us and see you all on Saturday.
